modName: METAL GEAR SOLID Snake eater Naked Snake Preset
summary: A MGS:SE preset for skyrim: Jack/Naked snake/big boss/ishmael
descriptionHtml:
well, hello again
this time i bring a shitty version of Naked snake for (obviously) skyrim
i tried searching something about him and just finded nothing, so i did one by myself and i liked
i decided to post this preset for everyone who wants to play as Jack/john from Metal gear solid snake eater/ metak gear solid v: Ground zeroes/Metal gear Solid v:The Phanton Pain (at the "true" ending)
the mods you will need is:

Immersive armors by Hothtrooper44
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19733/
(Use the Green Bandana)

Bandit EyePatch by Ceekay9
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1874
(Use the Richt EyePatch)

SGHairPack
din't find the link for the mod, you guys probably will find at "Lover's lab" or at some random youtube video

and of course RaceMenu
====================================================================================
Armors/others used on the SS

Nightingale Prime HD by AnicentVampire and ZeroFrost
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28899
(don't use the Helmet, it will unequip the bandana and eyepatch)

Cloaks of skyrim by Noodles
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12092/

For the Desert on the screenshots i was at Alikir desert addeded by the "The Gray Cowl of nocturnal" mod to simulate afghanistan from  MGSV:TPP
The Gray cowl of Nocturnal By MannyGT
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64651/
=========================================
Probably few will know me from my other preset of Paz...

THIS INS'INT A 100% IDENTICAL PRESET!
author: HUEBRhuehue
